query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char, MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress, MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation FROM aka_name AS an, complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, company_name AS cn, info_type AS it, info_type AS it3, keyword AS k, movie_companies AS mc, movie_info AS mi, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, person_info AS pi, role_type AS rt, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND cn.id = mc.company_id AND it.id = mi.info_type_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND rt.id = ci.role_id AND n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = pi.person_id AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND (n.name like '%M%' OR n.name like '%V%' OR n.name like '%J%' OR n.name like '%O%' OR n.name like '%P%') AND (k.keyword like '%obsession%' OR k.keyword like '%escape%') AND it3.info in ('crazy credits','LD group genre','other works','keywords','LD sound encoding','books','LD certification','production dates') AND cct1.kind in ('crew','complete','complete+verified') AND (mc.note like '%Denmark%') AND t.production_year < 1990 AND cct2.kind in ('complete+verified','cast','complete') AND cn.country_code in ('pe','ht','cv','bi','tj','mt','do','sr','co','bm') AND (cn.name like '%Pixar Animation Studios%' OR cn.name like '%Miramax%' OR cn.name like '%Paramount Pictures%' OR cn.name like '%Amblin Television%') AND it.info in ('LD disc format','LD digital sound','where now','agent address','top 250 rank','LD analog left','birth date','taglines','LD audio noise','gross','LD number of sides','LD picture format','LD additional information','LD color information','LD master format','mpaa','LD spaciality','novel','books','LD category') AND mi.info in ('Russian','Inuktitut','Swiss German','Hungarian','Albanian','Croatian','Cantonese','Brazilian Sign Language') AND (an.name like '%A%') AND (chn.name like '%Jason Bourne%')
